i know i said i would be posting picture tonight, but as of yesterday i am feeling really sick so i won't be updating for a little bit but when i do, the pictures will be well worth it. sorry everyone.

ugh im sick and i have a shitload of packing to do. what a GREAT combination. 

15 days till i move!!

just thought i would pass this on to this journal since i put it in my other journal. im moving to melbourne florida on the 26. so if any of ya'll live there or close to there let me know, im gonna need someone to show me the ropes lol.

posting new pictures either tonight or tomorrow

just got done with my mass friends delete thing. if your still able to see my friends only posts, your fine. 

just a note to everyone who wants to be added....YOU HAVE TO ADD ME BACK. you can't just leave a comment saying that you want to be added and then not add me back when i add you. it just doesn't work like that. 

so please keep that in mind when you say you want to be added. 

Thanks

Jessica

i see already that i am going to have to do mass friends delete already. 

for everyone on my friends list, YOU HAVE TO ADD ME BACK!! (if ya'll added me first and i added you back you have nothing to worry about) this is for the people who asked to be added and when i did didn't add me back. so seriously, add me back when i add you. 

massive delete T-2 days

Jessica

just a note to everyone, even if i haven't left a comment saying that your added, i did add you. it takes too much time to comment to everyone lol.

this is also for future reference too.

ill be posting new pics again tonight too.
im not sure who i added and who i didn't add....so if you left a comment and i didn't add you, leave one on here so i know....thanks much!

this is my photo journal....it is friends only. if you want to see comment and i will add you back. please keep in mind i would like everyone who wants to be a part of this journal to be 18+ so please have your age listed in your info..if you don't, you will not be added. thanks much Jessica
